        "$description": "最弱分隔/禁用,非正文,≈黑23%"
      }
    },
    "accent": {
      "$description": "Blue — the ONLY hue. Garnish only: logo, primary button, send, 推荐 mark, sign-off ring, selected tab underline, deep-zone TOC indicator. Never a large fill.",
